         <abstract>
            <p>In this paper we present a modified version of the pseudospectral method for solving initial-boundary value systems of hyperbolic partial differential equations. We are able to avoid problems of instability by regularizing the boundary conditions. We prove the stability and convergence of our proposed scheme and obtain error estimates.</p>
          </abstract>
